message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet your specific needs. This exceptional item carries a significant value of $12000 to me, reflecting its unique features and the expertise poured into its creation. I am extending this opportunity to you at an exclusive price of $11000, aiming to ensure a mutually beneficial transaction. Please let me know if you would like to proceed with this offer.
